headline: Why CooperCompanies (COO) Shares Are Falling Today
summary: Shares of medical device company CooperCompanies (NASDAQ:COO) fell 3.2% in the afternoon session after Rothschild & Co Redburn lowered its price target on the stock to $92 from $95.
